title: 空岛spigot-1.8.8客户端崩溃
author: whx1024
txt_content:
错误报告：我简单看了一下好像是ASkyBlock的错误，但不知道怎么解决。
[19:42:10 信息]: [ASkyBlock] Loading warps...
[19:42:10 ERROR]: [ASkyBlock] ********* The Generator for ASkyBlock is not registered so the plugin cannot start ********
[19:42:10 ERROR]: [ASkyBlock] Make sure you have the following in bukki-服务器已被强制关闭-t.yml (case sensitive):
[19:42:10 ERROR]: [ASkyBlock] worlds:
[19:42:10 ERROR]: [ASkyBlock]   # The next line must be the name of your world:
[19:42:10 ERROR]: [ASkyBlock]   world:
[19:42:10 ERROR]: [ASkyBlock]     generator: ASkyBlock
先发这一小段

replies.author: lichi2050
replies.txt_content:
由于你没有安装地图生成器插件（例如Multiverse或Multiworld）插件无法加载该类型世界
如果不想安装这类型插件可以修改Bukkit.yml
worlds:
ASkyblock:
generator: ASkyBlock?复制代码
添加ASkyblock世界并设置生成器为ASkyblock
